{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/work/munkaportal.ro/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<style>\nc{\n  color: var(--accent-color);\n  display: inline-block;\n  font-weight: 700;\n}\ncentered{\n  text-align:center;\n}\njustify{\n  text-align:justify;\n}\n    Img{\n      border: solid 1px #fff;\n    }\n    Img:hover{\n      border: solid 2px var(--accent-color);\n    }\n    \n </style>\n<justify>\n<p>The munkaportal.ro was designed as a lightweight landing page for the jobp.eu portal. It is based on web technologies, like <c>html</c>, <c>css</c> and the good old <c>javascript</c>.  </p>\n<p>Even so, quite a few features was built in, like the <c>in house translation plugin</c>, which delivers the content on 4 languages.  </p>\n<p> Besides this and the <c>responsive slider</c>,  the brightest feature is the job post <c>form</c>, which isn't using any plugins or frameworks for form validation, but it handles with pure javascript. The form gets submitted to <c>google sheets</c>, which sends automatic notification to our admins.  </p>\n<p> All this done in pure <c>javascript</c>. Simply and fast.</p>\n</justify>\n<br />\n<br />\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 756px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 103.17460317460319%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f8451efabb40f4042327ad35b5985ae7/687c2/thumb-munkap-1.webp 189w,\n/static/f8451efabb40f4042327ad35b5985ae7/014bc/thumb-munkap-1.webp 378w,\n/static/f8451efabb40f4042327ad35b5985ae7/42545/thumb-munkap-1.webp 756w,\n/static/f8451efabb40f4042327ad35b5985ae7/81d2f/thumb-munkap-1.webp 1134w,\n/static/f8451efabb40f4042327ad